      Working assumption: the operating cast (Sarah aside, who is the buyer) sit as part of the <strong>BAU team for the platform</strong> in steady state. They are not project roles. Joe represents the supplier-side population, Aisha represents the clinical safety function, Priya represents the platform engineering function, David represents the commercial framework function, Ngozi represents the information governance function. Each function exists permanently once the platform is operational.
